		<div class="projects-central-column">
			<p style="float:left;">
			<strong>Linux Exploration and Advancement Program</strong><br/>
			The project that the HCC plans to work on for the coming year is based on <a href="http://www.linuxfromscratch.org/">Linux From Scratch</a>. Throughout the year the HCC will meet and distribute tasks among its members regularly. The objectives of this project are to learn more about the internal structure of Linux, introduce and utilize new technologies related with Linux and build a lightweight but powerful operating system.
			</p>			
			<p style="float:left;">
			<strong>Distributed Linux Cluster</strong><br/>
			Using four PS3's a computing cluster is being networked and configured. The aim is to enable higher speeds and calculation accuracy. We've so far built the nodes and are working to use the slave nodes during computation using the master machine.
			</p>			
